      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 protocol followed at a single load configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min, ambient conditions). Only one test condition evaluated; multi-load-level or multi-fixture variation not explored. Temperature and humidity documented. Gradation 2 achieved — below required Gradation 3. This is a known gap acknowledged in the overall credibility assessment."
