      "rationale": "FEA model geometry derived from CAD nominal with CMM-verified as-built dimensions. UHMWPE block fixture geometry reproduced in FEA. Screw insertion torque translated to equivalent pretension via calibrated torque-angle relationship. Direct traceability established for all primary inputs. Gradation 3 achieved."
